gic to summon and revive zombies so you can drown your opponent in a wave of the undead! Shop thousands of sellers for the best prices on Zombie World Order TCG cards, booster boxes, Special Packs, and more.\",\"categoryPageTitle\":\"TCGplayer - Buy Zombie World Order TCG cards, booster boxes, Special Packs, and more\",\"mpCanSearch\":true},{\"categoryId\":37,\"catalogGroupId\":1,\"categoryName\":\"The Caster Chronicles\",\"displayName\":\"The Caster Chronicles\",\"urlName\":\"the-caster-chronicles\",\"categoryDescription\":\"Your all-girls academy is run by ancient demons: time to play card games! Shop thousands of sellers for the best prices on The Caster Chronicles cards, starter decks, booster boxes, and more.\",\"categoryPageTitle\":\"TCGplayer - Buy The Caster Chronicles cards, starter decks, booster boxes, and more\",\"mpCanSearch\":true},{\"categoryId\":38,\"catalogGroupId\":1,\"categoryName\":\"My Little Pony CCG\",\"displayName\":\"My Little Pony CCG\",\"urlName\":\"my-little-pony-ccg\",\"categoryDescription\":\"Draw on your Friends, Resources, and other cards to solve Problems and discover the magic of friendship! Shop thousands of sellers for the best prices this side of Canterlot on My Little Pony CCG cards, theme decks, and more.\",\"categoryPageTitle\":\"TCGplayer - Buy My Little Pony CCG cards, theme decks, and more\",\"mpCanSearch\":true},{\"categoryId\":47,\"catalogGroupId\":1,\"categoryName\":\"Exodus TCG\",\"displayName\":\"Exodus TCG\",\"urlName\":\"exodus-tcg\",\"categoryDescription\":\"Become a Drifter and explore the world of Eeventide in this innovative game that uses rarity as a game mechanic! Shop thousands of sellers for the best prices on Exodus TCG cards, booster boxes, and more.\",\"categoryPageTitle\":\"TCGplayer - Buy Exodus TCG cards and booster boxes\",\"mpCanSearch\":true},{\"categoryId\":48,\"catalogGroupId\":1,\"categoryName\":\"Lightseekers TCG\",\"displayName\":\"Lightseekers TCG\",\"urlName\":\"lightseekers-tcg\",\"categoryDe